{
  "stem": "12447.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Came to a point that it was too dangerous for my sister to do that because she was much bigger already.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She had to wear a band-- an armband.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think the armband started from the age of 12 or 13.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But she had to wear the armband.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And being caught without the armband could get beaten up or even locked up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So it was too dangerous for her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Besides that, we spent one night on the gentile side, on the Aryan side.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Not always you were able to come into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There were certain times that you came to the ghetto and they would not let you out-- I mean, they would not let you in.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we had to kind of find a pretty decent German that would let the kids in without any problem.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I remember one night, there was some kind of a inspection or something.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You couldn't even get close to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we spent the whole night in a-- in an apartment house, in the hallway with my sister.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was quite dangerous for her to be there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my parents decided that she will not go out anymore.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I would be the only one that will go out if the possibility, the chance, came about.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I did sometimes, like, two-- sometimes even three rounds a day, I would go out of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had many ways.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I wasn't the only one because we kind of formed a group of children doing the contraband.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't know them personally, but I knew them by looking at them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And if they were carrying something out from-- into the ghetto, I could recognize them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were my kind of kids.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
